    <p class="description">LongShot is the cheapest long-form AI writer with real fact-checking built in. It is also <strong>not a publishing tool, not an editor, and not a finished article</strong>. After 30 days of side-by-side testing against Jasper and Koala AI, here is what LongShot is really worth — and the real total monthly cost most reviews skip.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">SG</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/siddharth-gangal/">Siddharth Gangal</a></span>
          <span class="meta-author-role">Founder · theStacc</span>
