      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="post-body-wrap">
    <div class="post-grid">
      <article class="post-content">
        <p class="lede-p"><strong>LongShot is the best $19/mo you can spend on an AI writer — and the worst $19/mo if you actually need finished articles.</strong> After 30 days inside Pro and Team, plus interviews with 9 paying users, here is the honest verdict, the real total monthly cost once writers and editors are factored in, and the five situations where LongShot genuinely earns its keep.</p>

