          <div class="callout-label">⚡ TL;DR — The 30-second verdict</div>
          <p><strong>Buy LongShot if</strong> you are a solo blogger or freelance writer who needs a fast, fact-checked first draft and is happy to edit and publish yourself. FactGPT alone is worth the $19. <strong>Skip LongShot if</strong> you need finished, ranked content delivered to your CMS — the real monthly cost lands at <strong>$2,419–$7,519</strong> once you add editors, optimisation, and publishing time. theStacc handles all of that from $99/mo.</p>
