            <a href="/demo/" class="cta-btn-inline">Get my free audit <span>→</span></a>
            <span class="cta-meta">24-hour delivery · No card</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 id="vs-stacc">theStacc vs LongShot — where we are honestly better (and worse)</h2>
        <p>We wrote this review. We compete. Read the comparison first so you can weigh everything that follows.</p>

        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table>
            <thead>
              <tr><th>Feature</th><th>LongShot</th><th>theStacc</th></tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>Starting price</td><td class="cell-yes">$19/mo (annual)</td><td>$99/mo</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Fact-checking with citations</td><td class="cell-yes">FactGPT — best in class</td><td>Built into the editorial layer</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Articles written for you</td><td class="cell-no">No — AI drafts only</td><td class="cell-yes">30 finished articles/mo</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Human editing included</td><td class="cell-no">No</td><td class="cell-yes">Every article reviewed</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Auto-publishes to your CMS</td><td class="cell-no">Manual export only</td><td class="cell-yes">WordPress · Webflow · Ghost</td></tr>
              <tr><td>SERP-based content scoring</td><td class="cell-no">Basic SEO module</td><td class="cell-yes">Surfer-grade optimisation</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Google Business Profile posts</td><td class="cell-no">Not included</td><td class="cell-yes">30 GBP posts/mo</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Social posts (IG, LI, X, FB)</td><td class="cell-no">Not included</td><td class="cell-yes">30 posts/mo</td></tr>
