            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <p>Annual billing saves roughly 35% on Pro. Free trial gives enough credit to test one full article. No permanent free tier.</p>

        <h3>The real monthly cost most reviews skip</h3>

        <div class="cost-calc">
