          <div class="cons-card">
            <h4>✗ Where LongShot hurts</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>No SERP-based scoring — pair with Surfer / Clearscope ($79+/mo)</li>
              <li>No auto-publish — copy-paste to WordPress every time</li>
              <li>No human editing layer — drafts still need cleanup</li>
