          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-num">200k+</div>
            <div class="stat-lbl">Users since 2021</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3>Speed vs editing-time trade-off</h3>

        <div class="chart-card">
          <div class="chart-head">
            <div>
              <div class="chart-title">Editing time per 1,500-word draft (minutes)</div>
